Class WellingtonTrains

java.lang.Object
WellingtonTrains
public class WellingtonTrains extends Object
WellingtonTrains class maintains the UI for the Wellington Trains program.

The Wellington Trains class launches an interactive program that loads train station, line, and services data for the Wellington region.

Version:
1.1
Author:
Ronan Griffin griffirona@myvuw.ac.nz
